items.name: 12-Gauge Buckshot Shell
items.description: 12-Gauge Buckshot Shell, the basic ammunition used byShotguns. Unlike arrows, javelins, and bolts, this ammunition is destroyed on impact and cannot be recovered.

items.name: 12-Gauge CHAC Shell
items.description: 12-Gauge CHAC Shell is an advanced purchaseable buckshot ammunition that does up to 450 damage. It pairs well with theCHAC "Boomstick" Shotgunthat can also be purchased from theWorkshop.

items.name: 12-Gauge CHAC Shell Box
items.description: The 12-Gauge CHAC Shell Box provides 25 rounds of the12-Gauge CHAC Shellthat works with anyShotgunand pairs well with theCHAC "Boomstick" Shotgunthat can also be purchased from theWorkshop.

items.name: 12-Gauge Cold Steel Shell
items.description: 12-Gauge Cold Steel Shell is a Cold Steel variant of ammunition forShotguns. It inflicts extra Frost damage and a chance to slow the target and weaken their attacks.

items.name: 12-Gauge Explosive Shell
items.description: 12-Gauge Explosive Shells are used byShotguns. Unlike arrows, javelins, and bolts this ammunition is destroyed on impact and cannot be recovered. Damages area around target. Caution when using this ammunition is advised. 12-Gauge Explosive Shells have 6 pellets per shell.

items.name: 12-Gauge Miasmic Shell
items.description: 12-Gauge Miasmic Shell, a Miasmic variant of ammunition used byShotguns.

items.name: 12-Gauge Obsidian Shell
items.description: 12-Gauge Obsidian Shells are a variant of12-Gauge Buckshot Shellsthat deal fire damage on hit and have a chance to apply a unique debuff to targets while also setting them ablaze. Although it may have a low percent chance of setting targets on fire, 12-Gauge Obsidian Shells can decimate Fauna that have a weakness to fire, especially when the 'Burning' modifier occurs. A list of fauna that are weak to fire can be viewedhere.

items.name: 12.7mm CHAC Explosive Round
items.description: 12.7mm CHAC Explosive Round is a type of explosiveSniper Ammunitionfor theAnti-materiel Riflethat does 500 projectile damage and 400 explosive damage.

items.name: 12.7mm CHAC Incendiary Ammo Box

items.name: 9mm Round
items.description: The basic ammunition used by thePistols. Unlike arrows, javelins, and bolts this ammunition is destroyed on impact and cannot be recovered. With the talentPistol Proficiency, Prospectors can craft this ammo at a -25% reduced resource cost. Also, with the talentFreebies, Prospectors have a 5% chance to craft double ammo. The ability to craft double ammo works in tandem, on a successful proc chance, with the reduced resource cost recipe netting a total of six extra rounds of ammunition.

items.description: Columbian Mammoth Trophies are decorative deployables that can be placed on any wall surface and are used to liven any living space. items.name: Fire Arrow
items.description: Want to turn that forest filled with bears into an inferno? The fire arrow is your friend. Need a light at the top of that cave? Fire arrow. While not as bright as theFlare Arrow, it will continue burning upon impact. Similar to thePoison Arrow, the Fire Arrow is a DOT upgrade to theStone Arrow, which is helpful when in a 'fire and flee' situation. These arrows cannot be recovered once fired.
